description         Simple X hotkey daemon
long_description    ${name}: \
                    sxhkd is a simple X hotkey daemon with a powerful \
                    and compact configuration syntax.

checksums           rmd160  27c8013e4a57f1309f644f7b9c15a50351e14946 \
